SUMMARY:Live Music and Food Truck
DESCRIPTION:Live Music & Food Truck Night at Great Bear Vineyards in Davis \nFriday\, April 24 | 5–8pmTicket Includes: Glass of Wine & Live Music\nKick back and start your weekend the Great Bear way—with a glass of wine in hand and vineyard views all around. \nWe’ve got another beautiful Friday evening lined up featuring live music from the Wealth of Nations Duo\, bringing their signature laid-back\, feel-good sound to the vineyard. From Grateful Dead favorites to classic rock\, R&B\, and original songs\, their set is the perfect soundtrack for a relaxing night under the open sky. \n Come hungry! GyroStop will be onsite serving up fresh\, flavorful Mediterranean favorites—think gyro sandwiches\, falafel\, hummus\, and more—all crafted by Chef Ty and perfect for pairing with your favorite estate-grown wines.\nSip\, relax\, and settle in for an easygoing evening of great music\, delicious food\, and even better company.\n The perfect way to unwind and welcome the weekend—we can’t wait to see you there!
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/live-music-and-food-truck-18/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards 24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/Great-Bear-Vineyards_23GBV-drone-scaled-zK0eUQ.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
